$grp PS_MissionDescription : "{3136BE42592F3B1B}PrefabsEditable/MissionDescription/EditableMissionDescription.et" {
 {
  coords 2969.933 10 3021.631
  m_sTitle "SITUATION"
  m_sTextData "<b>Date:</b> 2020-07-06"\
  "<b>Location:</b> Kunar, Afghanistan"\
  ""\
  "Two months ago, U.S. forces operating in eastern Afghanistan were attacked by a newly emerging insurgent faction using improvised FPV drones carrying explosive payloads. The attack resulted in multiple casualties and marked the first mass use of locally manufactured strike drones in the region."\
  ""\
  "Subsequent ISR flights and human intelligence have identified the likely source of these drones - a concealed manufacturing and assembly facility located on the outskirts of the village of Gulahy Shal."\
  ""\
  "Tonight, a platoon from the 75th Ranger Regiment will conduct a night air assault to neutralize the facility before additional drone attacks can be carried out against U.S. forces in the region."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
 }
 {
  coords 2972.84 10 3019.835
  m_sTitle "MISSION"
  m_sTextData "At <b>0130</b> local, Ranger forces (029 030) will conduct an air assault raid on the objective compound (033 003) in order to:"\
  ""\
  "- <b>Destroy the insurgents' drone caches located inside the drone factory</b> "\
  ""\
  "- <b>ISR shows that insurgents' communications and planning center is located on the second floor of the drone factory. Recover any intelligence releted to the shipping routes of the drone parts from the location.</b>"\
  ""\
  "- <b>Locate and destroy an ammunition and weapons cache located somewhere inside the village of Gulahy Shal</b>"\
  ""\
  "Mission critical information: "\
  ""\
  "<i>- Air strikes and gun runs on drone factory are prohibited until intelligence has been recovered from the location.</i>"\
  ""\
  "<i>- ISR has spotted no enemy movement in the hills surrounding the objective area and any such threats will be dealt with. Approximate area with recorded enemy presence has been provided.</i>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 {
  coords 2974.932 10 3018.347
  m_sTitle "FRIENDLY FORCES"
  m_sTextData "Primary assault force consists of one Ranger platoon with an attached demolitions element."\
  ""\
  "Friendly forces are blocking any enemy reinforcements west and north-east of the objective village."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 {
  coords 2976.988 10 3018.378
  m_sTitle "ENEMY FORCES"
  m_sTextData "Enemy strength at the objective is assessed to be at approximately 30 insurgent fighters."\
  ""\
  "The insurgents are armed primarily with Eastern Bloc small arms and are wearing a mix of civilian and military clothing."\
  ""\
  "The enemy has also demonstrated extensive ability to deploy <b>IED FPV drones</b>, which may be launched from within the village or nearby structures once the assault begins."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 {
  coords 2978.827 10 3017.532
  m_sTitle "AIR PACKAGE"
  m_sTextData "Insertion and extraction will be conducted via aircraft from the 160th Special Operations Aviation Regiment."\
  ""\
  "<b>Air package includes:</b>"\
  ""\
  "- 2x AH-6M Little Birds armed with miniguns and dumbfire rockets."\
  "- 1x UH-60 Black Hawk armed with door-mounted miniguns."\
  "- 3x UH-60 Black Hawk transport helicopters."\
  ""\
  "<b>Suggested load plan:</b>"\
  ""\
  "Platoon HQ & Weapons Element -> Disco-1"\
  "Assault Element A -> Disco-2"\
  "Assault Element B -> Disco-3"\
  "Security Element -> Disco-4"\
  "Demolitions Team -> as per CO's intent."\
  ""\
  "<b>Suggested fold in:</b>"\
  ""\
  "After inserting the troops, it is suggested that pilots fold in to achieve the most with the assets at their disposal:"\
  ""\
  "Disco-2 -> Disco-1 (door gun operation and location based jamming)"\
  "Disco-3 -> Chaos-1 (camera pod operation and targeting)"\
  "Disco-4 -> Chaos-2 (camera pod operation and targeting)"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 {
  coords 2980.202 10 3016.823
  m_sTitle "ADMIN & SUPPLY"
  m_sTextData "Soldiers are equipped with their standard combat load."\
  ""\
  "A variety of weapon attachments are located at the airfield and are free to be used, 3x tactical ladders have also been provided."\
  ""\
  "No resupply or repair is available for the helicopters at this time."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 6
 }
 {
  coords 2981.322 10 3016.314
  m_sTitle "EW CAPABILITIES"
  m_sTextData "MH-60 Black Hawk transport helicopters have been furnished with non-removable drone jammers. "\
  ""\
  "You can expect the drone signal to start to degrade when they enter ~200m wide interference bubble centered around the helicopter. The drone becomes uncontrolable as it approaches the center of the interference area."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 7
 }
 {
  coords 2982.823 10 3015.453
  m_sTitle "MM NOTES (PLEASE READ)"
  m_sTextData "MM intent is for Blufor to conduct a fast raid on to the objectives. Approximate AO where you can expect to meet resistance has been provided so there is no need to land far away."\
  ""\
  "<b>Due to an issue I was not able to solve, specialty roles equiped with secondary weapons must drop them on the ground for them to become accesible.</b>"\
  ""\
  "Sources of light such as: lampposts, lamps etc. are mostly destructable."\
  ""\
  "Caches in all locations look like stacks of green crates."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 9
 }
 {
  coords 2984.78 10 3014.106
  m_sTitle "COMSIG"
  m_sTextData "<b>Platoon net:</b> 48.0 MHz"\
  "<b>Air net:</b> 49.0 MHz"\
  ""\
  "<b>Callsigns:</b>"\
  ""\
  "Platoon HQ : Blazer White 1"\
  "Assault Element A : Blazer White 2"\
  "Assault Element B : Blazer White 3"\
  "Security Element : Blazer White 4"\
  "Weapons Element : Blazer White 5"\
  "Demolition Team : Blazer White 6"\
  ""\
  "<b>Aviation Callsigns:</b>"\
  ""\
  "JTAC: Music"\
  "Lead attack : Chaos-1"\
  "Secondary attack : Chaos-2"\
  "Lead armed transport : Disco-1"\
  "Transport : Disco-2"\
  "Transport : Disco-3"\
  "Transport : Disco-4"\
  ""\
  "<i>IR strobes are available for aerial identification.</i>"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
 {
  coords 3362.596 310.289 456.497
  m_sTitle "END CONDITIONS"
  m_sTextData "- 85% Blufor killed"\
  "- 95% Opfor killed"\
  "- Completion of Blufor objectives"
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 8
 }
}
